---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import SlideIn from '@effects/SlideIn.astro';
---

<Layout title="Urban Oasis \\\\ Let's cultivate community.">
  <main>
    <header class="fixed top-0 z-50 w-full px-4 md:px-10">
      <SlideIn>
        <div class="container mx-auto opacity-95">
          <a href="#"><img src="urbanoasis-tall.png" alt="" class="h-20 md:h-28" /></a>
        </div>
      </SlideIn>
      <!-- <div class="bg-zinc-950 py-0.5"></div> -->
    </header>
    <div
      class="bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(49,84,44,1),rgba(16,71,52,0.5)),url('gardening-3.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center pb-16 pt-64 lg:pb-24 lg:pt-80"
    >
      <header class="fixed top-0 z-40 w-full bg-clip-text backdrop-blur-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center bg-zinc-950 opacity-60">
          <div class="h-16 md:h-20"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="bg-zinc-950 py-0.5"></div> -->
      </header>
      <div class="px-4 md:px-10">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-2xl text-lime-100 md:text-3xl">
            Let's<br />cultivate<br /><span class="text-5xl font-bold md:text-8xl">\\community.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <header class="sticky top-2 z-40 md:top-4">
      <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 -z-10 h-16 w-1/2 bg-zinc-200 md:h-20"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="flex h-16 items-center justify-end bg-zinc-200 px-4 md:h-20 md:px-10">
          <h2 class="text-underline text-end text-2xl font-bold md:text-4xl">MISSION</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div id="mission" class="-mt-16 bg-zinc-100 md:-mt-20">
      <div class="h-16 w-full bg-zinc-200 md:h-20"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto flex items-center justify-between gap-20 px-4 py-16 md:px-10">
        <div class="max-w-prose">
          <div class="space-y-6 text-xl">
            <p>
              Gardening holds immense potential in addressing the pressing issue of food insecurity while simultaneously
              fostering community connections and encouraging healthy lifestyles. We envision a brighter future where
              sustainable and flourishing gardens become a reality, starting in the Indianapolis area.
            </p>
            <p>
              The ability to grow a diverse range of fruits, vegetables, and herbs enables communities to become more
              self-reliant. By cultivating their own produce, individuals can reduce dependence on external food sources
              and ensure access to fresh, nutritious food year-round.
            </p>
            <p>
              Beyond addressing food insecurity, gardening forges tight-knit relationships among community members.
              Working together in shared garden spaces fosters a sense of unity and togetherness, promoting a supportive
              network where individuals can exchange ideas, recipes, and traditions.
            </p>
            <p>
              Moreover, gardening serves as a catalyst for cultivating healthy living. Engaging in physical activity
              while gardening provides numerous health benefits. Additionally, it encourages us to consume a more
              nutritious diet with firsthand access to fresh produce rich in vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-md bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-200 to-yellow-950">
          <img src="gardening-2.jpg" alt="" class="opacity-50" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <header class="sticky top-4 z-40 md:top-8">
      <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 -z-10 h-16 w-1/2 bg-lime-200 md:h-20"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="flex h-16 items-center justify-end bg-lime-200 px-4 md:mr-60 md:h-20 md:px-10">
          <h2 class="text-underline z-50 text-end text-2xl font-bold md:text-4xl">VOLUNTEER</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div id="volunteer" class="-mt-16 bg-lime-100 md:-mt-20">
      <div class="h-16 w-full bg-lime-200 md:h-20"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:px-10">
        <div class="max-w-prose">
          <div class="space-y-6 text-xl">
            <p>
              To turn this vision into reality, we extend an invitation for you to join us on this transformative
              journey. Together, we can create sustainable and thriving gardens throughout the Indianapolis area,
              strengthening community bonds and promoting healthier lifestyles.
            </p>
            <p>
              Whether you have prior gardening experience or are new to this fulfilling endeavor, your involvement will
              contribute to the collective success of our gardening initiatives. Let us join forces, sow the seeds of
              change, and cultivate a better future for everyone in our community here in Indianapolis.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <form action="">
          <label for=""></label>
          <input type="text" />
        </form>

        <div class="py-80"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
